    {
      "id": "G99xwWNtSLVOg6n-rJ0Vh",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 557,
      "y": 419,
      "width": 790.1194458007812,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aB",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1218855718,
      "version": 117,
      "versionNonce": 1882451430,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1766257354314,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "A flow is the foundational data processing concept in SDP which supports both \nstreaming and batch semantics. \n\nA flow reads data from a source, applies user-defined processing logic, \nand writes the result into a target. ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A flow is the foundational data processing concept in SDP which supports both \nstreaming and batch semantics. \n\nA flow reads data from a source, applies user-defined processing logic, \nand writes the result into a target. ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "-PSNUlrZ6UygPDcyLyRj4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 275,
      "y": 736,
      "width": 256.97283935546875,
      "height": 348.59523809523796,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aC",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 455187194,
      "version": 222,
      "versionNonce": 1676348390,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1766291204765,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\nA streaming table \nis a Delta table with\n additional support \nfor streaming \nor incremental data \nprocessing. \nA streaming table \ncan be targeted \nby one or more \nflows in a pipeline.",
      "fontSize": 25.352380952380944,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\nA streaming table \nis a Delta table with\n additional support \nfor streaming \nor incremental data \nprocessing. \nA streaming table \ncan be targeted \nby one or more \nflows in a pipeline.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
